  <description type="morphology">Cells of the mid-limb lamina (6–)7–10(–12) µm wide (mean 8.5 µm); cells of distal part of leaf sheath non-papillose on abaxial surface (rarely papillose in non-North American specimens).  Calyptra not persistent on seta.</description>
